subject: Basketball
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Epiphanny Prince scored a career-high 33 points, including 27 in the decisive second half, to lead Rutgers to a 73-71 victory Tuesday over top-ranked and previously unbeaten Connecticut.
